# рҹӣ’ TechStore вҖ” Full Stack E-Commerce Platform

A full-stack e-commerce web application built with **React**, **Node.js**, **Express**, and **MongoDB** вҖ” fully containerized with **Docker** and deployed on **AWS EC2** with a complete **CI/CD pipeline**.

рҹ”— **Live Demo:** [http://3.26.146.64](http://3.26.146.64)

---

## рҹ“ё Overview

TechStore is a real-world e-commerce platform where users can browse and purchase products online. The app is built with separate frontend and backend Docker images, orchestrated with Docker Compose, and automatically deployed to AWS EC2 via a CI/CD pipeline.

---

## рҹ§ұ Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| **Frontend** | React (Vite), HTML, CSS, JavaScript |
| **Frontend Server** | NGINX (serves the React production build) |
| **Backend** | Node.js, Express.js, JWT Authentication |
| **Database** | MongoDB + Mongo Express (admin UI) |
| **Containerization** | Docker, Docker Compose |
| **CI/CD** | GitHub Actions |
| **Cloud** | AWS EC2 |

---

