All services communicate over an isolated Docker bridge network (`app_network`). MongoDB data is persisted via a named Docker volume (`mongo-data`).

---

## вңЁ Features

- рҹ”җ User authentication вҖ” register & login with JWT
- рҹӣҚпёҸ Product listing page
- рҹӣ’ Shopping cart functionality
- рҹ“Ұ RESTful API backend
- вҡЎ Fast React + Vite frontend
- рҹҗі Multi-container setup with Docker Compose
- рҹ—„пёҸ MongoDB with Mongo Express admin panel
- вҳҒпёҸ Deployed on AWS EC2
- рҹ”„ Automated CI/CD pipeline via GitHub Actions

---

## рҹ”„ CI/CD Pipeline

The project uses **GitHub Actions** to automate the full build and deployment workflow:

```
Push to main branch
        в”Ӯ
        в–ј
в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ
в”Ӯ  GitHub Actions   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ                   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 1. Build frontend в”Ӯ  вҶ’ docker build вҶ’ push to Docker Hub
в”Ӯ    Docker image   в”Ӯ    (shusillimbu/frontend:latest)
в”Ӯ                   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 2. Build backend  в”Ӯ  вҶ’ docker build вҶ’ push to Docker Hub
в”Ӯ    Docker image   в”Ӯ    (shusillimbu/backend:latest)
в”Ӯ                   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 3. SSH into EC2   в”Ӯ  вҶ’ docker compose pull
в”Ӯ    & redeploy     в”Ӯ    docker compose up -d
в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ
```

---

## рҹҗі Running Locally

### Prerequisites
- [Docker](https://docs.docker.com/get-docker/) and [Docker Compose](https://docs.docker.com/compose/) installed

### Steps

```bash
# 1. Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/ShusilLimbu/TechStore.git
cd techstore

# 2. Start all services
docker compose up -d

# 3. Access the app
#    Frontend:      http://localhost
#    Backend API:   http://localhost:3000
#    Mongo Express: http://localhost:8081
```

**Mongo Express credentials:**
- Username: `mongoexpressuser`
- Password: `mongoexpresspass`

