## рҹҢҗ Services & Ports

| Service | Container Name | Port |
|---|---|---|
| React Frontend (NGINX) | `frontend-service` | `80` |
| Node.js Backend | `backend_service` | `3000` |
| MongoDB | `mongo` | `27017` |
| Mongo Express | `mongo-express` | `8081` |

---

## рҹҡҖ Deployment (AWS EC2)

The app is deployed on an **AWS EC2** instance (Ubuntu):

1. EC2 instance provisioned with Docker and Docker Compose installed
2. Inbound rules opened for ports `80`, `3000`, `8081`
3. GitHub Actions SSHs into the instance on every push to `main`, pulls the latest images, and restarts the containers

